Text: I have kept that sentiment of fighting for lost causes close to my heart throughout this campaign, literally. At the start of the campaign, I asked my parents for a St. Jude medallion, the patron saint of lost causes, and I've worn it every day. https://t.co/ySCbjXTgyj
